name: Imaginary Vagina 11/1
description: My story about imaginary vaginas formed in my mind and taken from the imaginary world of my sex, I have cut and collaged pieces of newspapers with sentences related to sex and lust or against sex freedoms in Islamic countries. And I worked on it with acrylic and magic paint and edited it in Photoshop software to finally turn it into what I wanted to be Nude art, this work is part of a collection (Number 11 of collection 1), that collectors and buyers can make the original work Receive physically
